import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, TextField, Button, Box } from '@mui/material';

function LoginSignup() {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="sm" id="login" sx={{ paddingY: 5 }}>
      <Box
        sx={{
          backgroundColor: '#C8A57F',
          padding: 4,
          borderRadius: 2,
          boxShadow: 3,
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom textAlign="center">
          Log In or Create an Account
        </Typography>
        <TextField
          label="Email"
          variant="outlined"
          fullWidth
          margin="normal"
          sx={{ backgroundColor: '#ffffff', borderRadius: 1 }}
        />
        <TextField
          label="Password"
          type="password"
          variant="outlined"
          fullWidth
          margin="normal"
          sx={{ backgroundColor: '#ffffff', borderRadius: 1 }}
        />
        <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" fullWidth sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
          Log In
        </Button>
        <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" fullWidth sx={{ mt: 2 }} href="#signup">
          Create Account
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default LoginSignup; // Ensure this is a default export
